					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I was going to announce the inauguration of a new member, and make a major event out of it.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"今天还有一个介绍新成员的大活动。",
					{"rt2"},
